XML-Xerces-BagOfTricks version 0.01
===================================

This module is designed to provide a bag of tricks for users of 
XML::Xerces. To start with it provides some useful variables for 
looking up xerces-c enum values. There should also be a small
selection of useful functions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  XML::Xerces

